  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#183049">Dangit!  I keep remembering stuff right after I post! 8)<br>
<br>
My original reason for sending this in and not keeping it a secret for myself (ehehe!) was to inspire more people to try out evil Gnome/Human Clerics and other odd combinations, in hopes that the servers won't be as saturated with Wood Elf Druids (heaven only knows how many people play those...) and people will be encouraged to take a different path that may not offer the most flashy spells or the coolest-looking race, or the ability to solo best, but instead suits their personality better.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Here's to hoping that I won't think of something else after I hit that darned "Submit" button!<br><br></td></tr>
